 word <i>miles</i> ‘soldier’ because of the military attributes of the archangel Michael. However, the usual Latin form of the name in the Middle Ages was <i>Milo</i>. There is a common Slavic name element <i>mil</i> ‘grace, favour’, with which it may possibly have some connection. The name has been in regular use in England since the 16th century.  See also  Milo   and   Myles ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs Miles Radcliffe was born in 1202, in England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 daughter with Miles de Radcliffe."},"et":{"1202–":"1202–Surnud","1200–Male":"1200–Surnud","1222–Female":"1222–Surnud","1202–Female":"1202–Surnud","1202":"1202","1222":"1222","1200":"1200","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1202–":"1202–Kuollut","1200–Male":"1200–Kuollut","1222–Female":"1222–Kuollut","1202–Female":"1202–Kuollut","1202":"1202","1222":"1222","1200":"1200","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England","England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1202–":"1202–Décédée","1200–Male":"1200–Décédé","1222–Female":"1222–Décédée","1202–Female":"1202–Décédée","1202":"1202","1222":"1222","1200":"1200","Yorkshire, England":"Everwyck, Angleterre","England":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mrs Miles Radcliffe est née en 1202, à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fille avec Miles de Radcliffe."},"de":{"1202–":"1202–Verstorben","1200–Male":"1200–Verstorben","1222–Female":"1222–Verstorben","1202–Female":"1202–Verstorben","1202":"1202","1222":"1222","1200":"1200","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England","England":"England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Mrs Miles Radcliffe wurde 1202 in England, United Kingdom geboren. Sie hatte mit Miles de Radcliffe mindestens 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"1202–":"1202–Desede","1200–Male":"1200–Desede","1222–Female":"1222–Desede","1202–Female":"1202–Desede","1202":"1202","1222":"1222","1200":"1200","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England","England":"Angletè, United Kingdom"},